# xkcd-mcp — Cursor rules

## Central documentation (read first)

Fleet standards live in **MCP Central Docs** (local clone):

`D:\Dev\repos\mcp-central-docs\`

**Hub:** `standards\AGENT_PROTOCOLS.md`.

**Most relevant:**

- `standards\SOTA_REQUIREMENTS.md` — FastMCP **3.1+**
- `standards\TOOL_DESIGN_STANDARDS.md` — portmanteau tools, docstrings
- `standards\WEBAPP_STANDARDS.md` — webapp ports **10700–10800**; this project **10778** / **10779**
- `operations\WEBAPP_PORTS.md` — port registry
- `standards\PACKAGING_STANDARDS.md` — uv, justfile, `llms.txt` + `llms-full.txt`, glama

## Shell (Windows)

PowerShell: use `;` to chain commands; avoid bash-only syntax in scripts.
